{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a5730b9179","title":"“三害”判决书","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"dc1096180f","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"a5730b9179"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19f3f1b8ea","name":"北京大学"},{"id":"599fa55c22","name":"张志武"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e6087fc3b1","type":"title","text":"“三害”判决书","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a5730b9179"},{"id":"73dbb237d7","type":"authors","text":"北京大学张志武","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a5730b9179"},{"id":"eea228573b","type":"subtitle","text":"（张志武：北京大学法律系学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a5730b9179"},{"id":"0bc5283385","type":"paragraph","text":"被告：宗派主义，年36岁，1921年7月1日生","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a5730b9179"},{"id":"474e02cd3d","type":"paragraph","text":"教条主义，年38岁，1919年5月4日生","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a5730b9179"},{"id":"bebfb0802a","type":"paragraph","text":"官僚主义，年8岁，1949年10月1日生","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a5730b9179"},{"id":"eec836a4ba","type":"paragraph","text":"查被告宗派主义自诞生以来，搞不团结，破坏党与非党团结迫害群众，造成对党不满。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a5730b9179"},{"id":"742bd5ed67","type":"paragraph","text":"查被告教条主义，将马克思主义当成死的圣经，不问客观情况，硬按清规戒律行事，不顾中国情况，生搬硬套苏联经验，扼杀新生力量。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a5730b9179"},{"id":"ca976385fd","type":"paragraph","text":"查被告官僚主义，平日高高在上，不问下情，主观臆断，脱离人民，在这次整风运动中，对来自群众的批评置之不理，反恶意猜测提意见的动机；加以打击报复。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a5730b9179"},{"id":"bfa3d30de5","type":"appellation","text":"以上被告由北京大学全体学生公诉来院，经本院审讯被告对以上罪行供认不讳。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a5730b9179"},{"id":"b6d9e64cb7","type":"paragraph","text":"为了整风，彻底根除三害，现应判处被告死刑，但念宗派主义对加强党性，维护党的利益，保持党的纯洁有功。教条主义虽然生搬教条，但对减轻脑力劳动，防止操劳过度，遵守马列主义则有功。官僚主义对维获领导威信，防止忙于日常琐事有功，减干部体力劳动过度有功，故免于判刑宣布无罪释放，今后再有骚乱滋事之徒控告那三个主义，本院定判其诬告罪，斩首公众，以儆效尤。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a5730b9179"},{"id":"d1b2f6097c","type":"paragraph","text":" 北京大学整风法院附：此件约于6月上旬拟就。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a5730b9179"},{"id":"a258a88e7f","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：北京大学社会主义思想教育委员会编印《北京大学右派分子反动言论汇集》，一九五七年十月。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a5730b9179"}],"page":{"id":"7ecccb3606","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a5730b9179","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}